  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;China has expressed a desire to make a positive contribution to global environmental challenges. China&#x2019;s huge portfolio of overseas investments under the Belt and Road Initiative stands to make or break the targets of the Paris Agreement. This grant supports ClientEarth&#x2019;s work to strengthen environmental law in China and mitigate the climate and environmental impacts of China&#x2019;s overseas trade and investment. Under the China program, this grant also supports capacity development for environmental judges and prosecutors, and nurtures the newly established NGO capacity-building fund. (Substrategy: China National Policy)&quot;</narrative>
  </description>
